revision.text:
Quests can be completed to earn [[Quest Points]], which can in turn be used to purchase eggs, evolution items, and other collectibles.
===Tutorial=== {| class="wikitable" |- ! Type !! Requirement !! Reward |- | Defeat Pokémon || Defeat Your Starter || 10 [[Quest Points]] |- | Capture Pokémon || Capture 1 Pokémon || 20 [[Quest Points]] |- | Defeat Pokémon || Defeat 5 Pokémon on Route 2 || 20 [[Quest Points]] |- | Purchase Item || Buy 10 Pokeballs || 50 [[Quest Points]] |- | Purchase Item || Buy [[Dungeon Ticket]] || Access to [[Dungeons]] |- | Clear Dungeon || Clear Viridian Forest || 50 [[Quest Points]] |- | Defeat Gym || Beat Brock || 50 [[Quest Points]] |- |}
===Normal Quests=== {| class="wikitable" |- ! Type/Requirement !! Range of Requirements !! Rough Reward |- | Defeat Pokémon || Between 100 and 500 Pokémon on an unlocked Route || Pokémon * 1 [[Quest Points]] |- | Capture Pokémon || Between 100 and 500 Pokémon || Pokémon * 1.25 [[Quest Points]] |- | Gain Money || Between 20,000 and 60,000 {{pdollar}} || Money * .0017 [[Quest Points]] |- | Gain [[Dungeon Tokens]] || Between 1,000 to 8,000 {{Dungeontokens}} || Tokens * .1 [[Quest Points]] |- | Gain [[Shards]] || Between 200 and 600 Shards of either Normal, Poison, Water, Grass, Fire, Fighting or Flying type || Shards * 1 [[Quest Points]] |- | Hatch Eggs || Between 1 and 30 eggs || Eggs * 33 [[Quest Points]] |- | Mine Layer || Between 1 and 3 layers || Layers * 720 [[Quest Points]] |- | Catch [[Shinies]] || 1 shiny || [[Shinies]] * 3000 [[Quest Points]] |- | Defeat Gym || Between 5 and 20 clears for an unlocked gym || [[Quest Points]] |- | Defeat Dungeon || Between 5 and 20 clears for an unlocked dungeon || [[Quest Points]] |- | Use a type of Pokeball || Between 100 and 500 Pokéballs, Greatballs, or Ultraballs || [[Quest Points]] |- | Use an [[Oak Item]] X times || Use either the [[Magic Ball]], [[Amulet Coin]], or [[EXP Share]] between 100 and 500 times || [[Quest Points]] |- | Harvest Berries || At least 30 Berries of of a type obtainable in the current region and takes less than 6 hours to ripen || [[Quest Points]] |}
===Deoxys Quest=== {| class="wikitable" |- ! Type !! Requirement !! Reward |- | Defeat Pokemon || Defeat 500 Psychic-type Pokemon || 500 Psychic [[Shards]] |- | Capture Pokemon || Catch 200 Psychic-type Pokemon || 20 Mind [[Plate|Plates]] |- | Battle Frontier || Beat Stage 100 of the Hoenn [[Battle Frontier]] || None (Deoxys auto-awarded by Battle Frontier) |}

Quests can be completed to earn [[Quest Points]], which can in turn be used to purchase eggs, evolution items, and other collectibles.
===Tutorial=== {| class="wikitable" |- ! Type !! Requirement !! Reward |- | Defeat Pokémon || Defeat Your Starter || 10 [[Quest Points]] |- | Capture Pokémon || Capture 1 Pokémon || 20 [[Quest Points]] |- | Defeat Pokémon || Defeat 5 Pokémon on Route 2 || 20 [[Quest Points]] |- | Purchase Item || Buy 10 Pokeballs || 50 [[Quest Points]] |- | Purchase Item || Buy [[Dungeon Ticket]] || Access to [[Dungeons]] |- | Clear Dungeon || Clear Viridian Forest || 50 [[Quest Points]] |- | Defeat Gym || Beat Brock || 50 [[Quest Points]] |- |}
===Normal Quests=== {| class="wikitable" |- ! Type/Requirement !! Range of Requirements !! Rough Reward |- | Defeat Pokémon || Between 100 and 500 Pokémon on an unlocked Route || Pokémon * 1 [[Quest Points]] |- | Capture Pokémon || Between 100 and 500 Pokémon || Pokémon * 1.25 [[Quest Points]] |- | Gain Money || Between 20,000 and 60,000 {{pdollar}} || Money * .0017 [[Quest Points]] |- | Gain [[Dungeon Tokens]] || Between 1,000 to 8,00 {{Dungeontokens}} || Tokens * .1 [[Quest Points]] |- | Gain [[Shards]] || Between 200 and 600 Shards of either Normal, Poison, Water, Grass, Fire, Fighting or Flying type || Shards * 1 [[Quest Points]] |- | Hatch Eggs || Between 1 and 30 eggs || Eggs * 33 [[Quest Points]] |- | Mine Layer || Between 1 and 3 layers || Layers * 720 [[Quest Points]] |- | Catch [[Shinies]] || 1 shiny || [[Shinies]] * 3000 [[Quest Points]] |- | Defeat Gym || Between 5 and 20 clears for an unlocked gym || [[Quest Points]] |- | Defeat Dungeon || Between 5 and 20 clears for an unlocked dungeon || [[Quest Points]] |- | Use a type of Pokeball || Between 100 and 500 Pokéballs, Greatballs, or Ultraballs || [[Quest Points]] |- | Use an [[Oak Item]] X times || Use either the [[Magic Ball]], [[Amulet Coin]], or [[EXP Share]] between 100 and 500 times || [[Quest Points]] |- | Harvest Berries || At least 30 Berries of of a type obtainable in the current region and takes less than 6 hours to ripen || [[Quest Points]] |}
===Deoxys Quest=== {| class="wikitable" |- ! Type !! Requirement !! Reward |- | Defeat Pokemon || Defeat 500 Psychic-type Pokemon || 500 Psychic [[Shards]] |- | Capture Pokemon || Catch 200 Psychic-type Pokemon || 20 Mind [[Plate|Plates]] |- | Battle Frontier || Beat Stage 100 of the Hoenn [[Battle Frontier]] || None (Deoxys auto-awarded by Battle Frontier) |}
